This week focused on understanding the fundamentals of Python.
I learned about:

Variables & Data Types: int, float, string, list, bool, etc.

Operators: arithmetic, logical, comparison, and assignment.

Input/Output: using input() and print().

Conditional Statements: if, elif, and else.

Loops: for and while loops for iteration.
